The paper presents a framework for safe learning using adaptive model learning and barrier certificates for systems with nonstationary agent dynamics. This involves reinforcement learning, optimization, and control theory. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.RO (Robotics), cs.SY (Systems and Control), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
